  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.esa.int/esaCP/"&gt;European Space Agency&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://news.bis.gov.uk/Press-Releases/Government-to-invest-20-million-in-synthetic-biology-682fa.aspx"&gt;Press notice: Government to invest £20 million in synthetic biology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bbsrc.ac.uk/news/research-technologies/2012/121109-pr-investment-uk-synthetic-biology-research.aspx"&gt;Biotechnology &amp;amp; Biological Research Council (BBSRC) Press Notice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
