  &lt;li&gt;On February 7 the Prime Minister announced &lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk//news/topstories/2012/Feb/apprenticeships-government-funding"&gt;round two of the Higher Apprenticeship Fund&lt;/a&gt;
